(11, 'Les ssr farmables AGI', '<p>Bonjours &agrave; tous, voici un petit guide destin&eacute; aux d&eacute;butants visant &agrave; savoir si les SSR qu&rsquo;on peut r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer &agrave; travers les diff&eacute;rents &eacute;v&eacute;nements valent le coup et si ils ont la place dans leur</p>\r\n\r\n<p>diff&eacute;rentes compositions &agrave; travers 5&nbsp;points :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Leur r&ocirc;le</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Les pours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Les contres</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Les &eacute;v&eacute;nements dans lesquels ils ont un atout cl&eacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Un score <em>(Correct &agrave; partir de 8, bon &agrave; partir de 14, excellent au dessus de 18)&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pour la note, j&rsquo;ai d&eacute;cid&eacute; d&rsquo;utiliser un bar&egrave;me, afin que la note de chaque persos soit la plus objective possible</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://img4.hostingpics.net/pics/393575Capturedecran20170406a184006.png" onclick="javascript:window.open(''https://img4.hostingpics.net/pics/393575Capturedecran20170406a184006.png''); return false;"><img src="https://img4.hostingpics.net/pics/563542Capturedecran20170407a141733.png" style="height:888px; width:1053px" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>N&rsquo;h&eacute;sitez pas &agrave; me corriger si j&rsquo;ai commis des erreurs ou oubli&eacute; des persos !!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/dbz-dokkanbattle/images/5/5a/AGL_icon.png/revision/latest?cb=20150825230835" style="height:130px; width:130px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Les SSR AGI gratuits :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href="https://dbz-dokkanbattle.wikia.com/wiki/Limitless_Energy_Androids_17_%26_18" onclick="javascript:window.open(''https://dbz-dokkanbattle.wikia.com/wiki/Limitless_Energy_Androids_17_%26_18''); return false;">C17 &amp; C18 LR</a> / Invocations Ami + 15 Dokkan Events&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/dbz-dokkanbattle/images/7/7f/LR_17_18.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/250?cb=20160915212132" style="height:354px; width:250px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>R&ocirc;le : Cogneur / Leader\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Ki + 4 Rainbow</li>\r\n		<li>ATT + 15k lors d&rsquo;une ATT SP</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Les pours :\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Moyenne des stats 11133 (+ 11 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Leader Ki+4 Rainbow (H.C. + 5 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>D&eacute;g&acirc;ts Titanesque SP20 (+ 5 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>ATT + 15000 &nbsp;(+ 7.5 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Baisse ATT ( + 5 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Baisse DEF ( + 2 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Tr&egrave;s bon lien : Vitesse &eacute;poustouflante (+ 2.25 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Liens corrects : Innocent, Nightmare, Fear &amp; Faith (+ 2.25 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Ki multiplier de 200 (H.C. + 3 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Tr&egrave;s bonne synergie : 13100 d&rsquo;ATT pour un cogneur ( + 2 pt)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Les contres :\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Un seul bon lien (- 1 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Restriction sur la baisse d&rsquo;ATT &amp; DEF : 18 Ki ( &ndash; 2.1 pt)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Events cl&eacute; :\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Plan d&rsquo;extermination des h&eacute;ros (+ 0.5 pt)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Le score :<strong> 42.4&nbsp;</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Un leader skill unique. Ils font tr&egrave;s tr&egrave;s mal lorsqu&rsquo;ils partent en sp&eacute; ultime.</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href="https://dbz-dokkanbattle.wikia.com/wiki/Ingenious_Collaboration_Androids_17_%26_18" onclick="javascript:window.open(''https://dbz-dokkanbattle.wikia.com/wiki/Ingenious_Collaboration_Androids_17_%26_18''); return false;">C17 &amp; C18 LR (TUR)</a> / Invocations Ami + 10 Dokkan Events&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/dbz-dokkanbattle/images/a/a7/Exquisite_Cooperation_Android_17_%26_18.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/250?cb=20161124225503" style="height:332px; width:250px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>R&ocirc;le : Cogneur / Leader\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Ki+3 Rainbow</li>\r\n		<li>ATT +10k lors d&rsquo;une ATT SP</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Les pours :\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Moyenne des stats 7325 (+ 6 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Leader Ki+3 Rainbow (H.C. + 3 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>D&eacute;g&acirc;ts Colossaux SP10 (+ 3 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>ATT + 10000 &nbsp;(+ 5 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Tr&egrave;s bon lien : Vitesse epoustouflante (+ 2.25 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Liens corrects : Innocent, Nightmare, Fear &amp; Faith (+ 2.25 pt)</li>\r\n		<li>Bonne synergie : 8023 d&rsquo;ATT pour un cogneur (+ 1 pt)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Les contres :\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Un seul bon lien (- 1 pt)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Events cl&eacute; :\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Plan d&rsquo;extermination des h&eacute;ros (+ 0.5 pt)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Le score : <strong>22</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Sous cette forme , la carte commence &agrave; avoir sa place dans beaucoup de compo AGI</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt="" src="https://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/dbz-dokkanbattle/images/9/95/Japan_server.png/revision/latest?cb=20150930163423" style="height:32px; width:32px" /></strong><strong>&nbsp;<a href="https://dbz-dokkanbattle.wikia.com/wiki/Threat_of_Erosion_Super_Baby_1" onclick="javascript:window.open(''https://dbz-dokkanbattle.wikia.com/wiki/Threat_of_Erosion_Super_Baby_1''); return false;">Super Baby 1</a>&nbsp;(TUR) / GT Baby Saga 1 &amp; 2&nbsp;</strong><strong><img alt="" src="https://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/dbz-dokkanbattle/images/9/95/Japan_server.png/revision/latest?cb=20150930163423" style="height:32px; width:32px" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/dbz-dokkanbattle/images/0/0a/Super_Baby_Vegeta.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/250?cb=20160828144731" style="height:333px; width:250px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Son r&ocirc;le :&nbsp;Cogneur &amp; Tank